---
import SectionHeader from "../primitives/SectionHeader.astro";
import { site } from "../../data/site";
---

<section id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <SectionHeader
      eyebrow="About"
      title={`About ${site.founder.name}`}
    />
    <div class="content about-body">
      <p>
        I built Escape Velocity AI because the system I needed didn't exist yet. I wanted a faceless YouTube channel — without a camera, without an editing rig, without trading my evenings for views. Every "AI content tool" I tried promised end-to-end production and shipped something I wouldn't publish under my own name.
      </p>
      <p>
        So I built the pipeline myself. Make.com orchestrates the handoffs. Claude writes the scripts. ElevenLabs handles the voice. InVideo AI does the visual assembly. Every step has a QA gate I designed to catch the failure modes I kept hitting. My own faceless channel is the live working demo, running the exact same pipeline you'd buy.
      </p>
      <p>
        What I sell is the system, not my time. I run it end-to-end myself, which keeps quality where it is — but it also caps how many channels I can take on. If you're reading this kit, you're early. The earlier you are, the more I can shape the pipeline around your specific business.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-body p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .about-body p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
</style>
